column5: Has anyone been to LacSuel Lodge in Ontario, Canada? If so, what time of the year and where do you fish??

David Lachowitzer,I'm fairly certain that my father has been there. I'm sure that if you have any questions about the western half Lac Seul, I'm sure that he would be more than happy to help you. I have been up there fishing a dozen times or so, but he usually gets up there 4 or 5 times a year! Lucky Guy... His E-mail is [email protected] Hope this helps a little.Matt N.
